# Frontend Rules

- Templates live in `ui/templates/`; extend `base.html` when adding pages.
- Static assets are in `ui/static/` (CSS, JS).
- Prefer HTMX patterns already used in the project for dynamic updates.
- Keep UI changes consistent with existing Tailwind/CSS conventions in `ui/static/css/`.
